<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='219:246'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-1a' );" name="007-1a" class="pb">[007-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='246:260'>禮記要義卷第八　文王丗子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='260:271'>　一文王一飯亦一飯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='271:291'>文王一飯亦一飯文王再飯亦再飯旬有二日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='291:309'>乃閒注云欲知氣力箴藥所勝間猶瘳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='309:319'>　二日三朝皆言朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='319:339'>内則云命士以上昧爽而朝日入而夕者朝禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='339:359'>具夕禮簡故言夕今三皆曰朝者以其禮同故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='359:379'>通言朝凡常丗子朝父母每日唯二今文王朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='379:399'>於王季日三者増一時又三者皆稱朝並是聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='399:426'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-1b' );" name="007-1b" class="pb">[007-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='426:432'>人之法也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='432:444'>　三文王損壽武王延年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='444:464'>古者謂年齡齒亦齡也我百爾九十吾與爾三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='464:484'>焉注云年天氣也齒人壽之數也九齡九十年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='484:504'>之祥也文王以勤憂損壽武王以安樂延年正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='504:524'>義曰皇氏云以九齡謂鈴鐸謂天以九箇鈴鐸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='524:544'>而與武王徧驗書本齡皆從齒解爲鈴鐸於理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='544:553'>有疑亦得爲一義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='553:563'>　四生壽不可増損</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='563:590'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-2a' );" name="007-2a" class="pb">[007-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='590:610'>年壽之數賦命自然不可延之寸隂不可减之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='610:630'>晷刻文王九十七武王九十三天定之數今文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='630:650'>王云吾與女三者示其傳基業於武王欲使武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='650:670'>王承其所傳之業此乃教戒之義訓非自然之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='670:673'>理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='673:682'>五成王踐阼之年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='682:702'>正義曰案鄭注金縢云文王崩後明年生成王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='702:722'>則武王崩時成王年十歳服䘮三年畢成王年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='722:742'>十二明年將踐阼周公欲代之攝政羣叔流言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='742:769'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-2b' );" name="007-2b" class="pb">[007-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='769:789'>周公辟之居東都時成王年十三也居東二年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='789:809'>成王收捕周公之屬黨時成王年十四也明年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='809:829'>秋大孰遭雷風之變時周公居東三年成王年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='829:849'>十五迎周公反而居攝之元年也居攝四年封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='849:869'>康叔作康誥是成王年十八也故書傳云天子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='869:889'>大子十八稱孟侯居攝七年成王年二十一也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='889:909'>明年成王即政年二十二也此是鄭義推成王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='909:919'>㓜不能踐阼之事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='919:930'>六鄭以大司成即師氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='930:957'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-3a' );" name="007-3a" class="pb">[007-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='957:977'>大司成論說在東序注云論說課其義之深淺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='977:997'>才能優劣此云樂正司業父師司成則大司成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='997:1017'>司徒之屬師氏也師氏掌以媺詔王教國子以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1017:1037'>三德三行及國中失之事也正義曰鄭以下文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1037:1057'>云樂正司業父師司成父師與樂正相連此大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1057:1077'>司成亦與大樂正相次故知司成則大司成也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1077:1097'>以其掌教故知是司徒之屬以其父師司成又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1097:1117'>掌教國子故知當師氏也引師氏以媺詔王以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1117:1137'>下者皆師氏職文案書傳大夫爲父師周禮師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1137:1164'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-3b' );" name="007-3b" class="pb">[007-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1164:1170'>氏中大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1170:1180'>七侍大司成間三席</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1180:1200'>凡侍坐於大司成者遠近間三席可以問終則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1200:1220'>負牆列事未盡不問注云間猶容也容三席則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1220:1240'>得指畫相分別也席之制廣三尺三寸三分則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1240:1260'>是所謂函丈也郤就後席相辟錯尊者之語不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1260:1264'>敬也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1264:1272'>　八釋奠先師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1272:1292'>凡學春官釋奠于其先師秋冬亦如之注云官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1292:1319'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-4a' );" name="007-4a" class="pb">[007-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1319:1339'>謂禮樂詩書之官周禮曰凡有道者有德者使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1339:1359'>教焉死則以爲樂祖祭於瞽宗此之謂先師之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1359:1379'>類也若漢禮有髙堂生樂有制氏詩有毛公書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1379:1399'>有伏生億可以爲之也不言夏夏從春可知也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1399:1414'>九釋奠無迎尸以下之事非報功</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1414:1434'>釋奠直奠置於物無食飲酬酢之事故云設薦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1434:1454'>饌酌奠而巳無迎尸以下之事釋奠所以無尸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1454:1467'>者以其主於行禮非報功也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1467:1476'>十釋奠與鄰國合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1476:1503'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-4b' );" name="007-4b" class="pb">[007-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1503:1523'>凡釋奠者必有合也有國故則否注云國無先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1523:1543'>聖先師則所釋奠者當與鄰國合也若唐虞有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1543:1563'>夔伯夷周有周公魯有孔子則各自奠之不合</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1563:1566'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1566:1578'><span class='krp-note'>十/一</span>郊學升𥙷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1578:1598'>凡語于郊者必取賢歛才焉或以德進或以事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1598:1618'>舉或以言揚曲藝皆誓之以待又語三而一有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1618:1637'>焉乃進其等以其序謂之郊人遠之於成均</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1637:1657'>以及取爵於上尊也注云語謂論說於郊學大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1657:1684'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-5a' );" name="007-5a" class="pb">[007-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1684:1704'>樂正論造士之秀者升諸司馬曰進士謂此矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1704:1724'>曲藝爲小技能也誓謹也皆使謹習其事又語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1724:1744'>爲後復論說也三說之中有一善則取之以有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1744:1764'>曲藝不必盡善進於衆學者又以其藝爲次俟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1764:1784'>事官之缺者以代之遠之者不曰俊選曰郊人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1784:1804'>賤技藝董仲舒曰五帝名大學曰成均則虞庠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1804:1824'>近是也天子飲酒于虞庠則郊人亦得酌于上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1824:1844'>尊以相旅正義曰謂之郊人者雖有次序而待</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1844:1865'>職缺當擬𥙷之若國子學士未官之前俱爲俊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1865:1892'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-5b' );" name="007-5b" class="pb">[007-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1892:1912'>選而以小才技藝者未官之前而不得同爲俊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1912:1934'>選但名曰郊人言其猶在郊學也　遠之者所以謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1934:1946'>爲郊人者是踈遠之故也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1946:1961'><span class='krp-note'>十/二</span>釋奠有六釋菜有三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1961:1983'>正義曰前用幣直云告器成此釋菜云告器成將用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1983:2006'>則兩告不同也熊氏云用幣則無菜用菜則無幣皇氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2006:2029'>云用幣釋菜秪是一告其義恐非也案四時釋奠不及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2029:2051'>先聖知此用幣及釋菜及先聖者以上文始立學釋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2051:2073'>奠先聖先師此文亦云始立學旣釁器用幣釋菜亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2073:2100'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-6a' );" name="007-6a" class="pb">[007-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2100:2120'>及先聖也以其始立學及器新成事重於四時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2120:2142'>常奠也故學記云皮弁祭菜鄭注禮先聖先師知及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2142:2164'>先聖者以彼云未卜禘不視學則祭菜與視學爲一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2164:2184'>也此下文云天子視學祭先聖先師故知學記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2184:2204'>祭菜及先聖也熊氏云月令釋菜不及先聖者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2204:2224'>以其四時入學釋菜故不及先聖也王制釋奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2224:2244'>于學注以爲釋菜奠幣知非釋奠者彼是告祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2244:2265'>之禮𥘉天子出師受成於學告之無牲明反告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2265:2285'>亦無牲也故謂釋奠時亦不及先聖也凡釋奠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2285:2312'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-6b' );" name="007-6b" class="pb">[007-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2312:2332'>有六始立學釋奠一也四時釋奠有四通前五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2332:2352'>也王制師還釋奠于學六也釋菜有三春入學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2352:2372'>釋菜合舞一也此釁器釋菜二也學記皮弁祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2372:2391'>菜三也秋頒學合聲無釋菜之文則不釋菜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2391:2411'>也釋幣唯一也即此釁器用幣是也以前皆熊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2411:2421'>氏之說義或當然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2421:2435'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>書傳天子有四鄰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2435:2455'>尚書大傳古者天子必有四鄰前曰疑後曰丞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2455:2475'>左曰輔右曰弼天子有問無以對責之疑可志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2475:2502'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-7a' );" name="007-7a" class="pb">[007-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2502:2522'>而不志責之丞可正而不正責之輔可揚而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2522:2540'>揚責之弼其爵視卿其禄視次國之君也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2540:2558'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>三命不踰父兄又三命不齒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2558:2578'>庶子治之雖有三命不踰父兄注云治之治公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2578:2598'>族之禮也唯於内朝則然其餘㑹聚之事則與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2598:2618'>庶姓同一命齒于郷里再命齒于父族三命不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2618:2645'>齒不齒者特爲位不在父兄行列中<span class='krp-note'>襄十二年/叔仲子引</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2645:2653'><span class='krp-note'>此義/異</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2653:2666'><span class='krp-note'>十/五</span>同宗不相賔客</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2666:2693'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-7b' );" name="007-7b" class="pb">[007-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2693:2713'>若公與族燕則異姓爲賔膳宰爲主人公與父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2713:2733'>兄齒注云同宗無相賔客之道君尊不獻酒親</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2733:2737'>親也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2737:2756'><span class='krp-note'>十/六</span>公宫大廟貴宫貴室下宫下室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2756:2776'>公若有岀疆之政庶子以公族之無事者守於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2776:2796'>公宫正室守大廟諸父守貴宫貴室諸子諸孫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2796:2816'>守下宫下室注云謂朝覲㑹同也正室適子也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2816:2836'>大廟大祖之廟謂守路寢下宫親廟也下室燕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2836:2848'>寢或言宫或言廟通異語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2848:2875'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-8a' );" name="007-8a" class="pb">[007-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2875:2892'><span class='krp-note'>十/七</span>天子内外朝及諸侯之朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2892:2912'>案周禮司士掌路寢門外之朝則知此内朝是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2912:2932'>路寢庭朝也外朝謂路寢門外之朝也若公族</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2932:2952'>在於外朝與異姓同處位次之時則以官之上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2952:2972'>下不復以年齒也司士爲之者謂司士之官主</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2972:2992'>爲朝位之次外朝位旣司士主之則内朝庶子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2992:3012'>主之也上文内朝不云庶子爲之者以文承庶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3012:3032'>子之下主之可知故不言也司士亦司馬之屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3032:3052'>也掌羣臣之班正朝儀之位也案周禮司士掌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3052:3079'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-8b' );" name="007-8b" class="pb">[007-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3079:3099'>正朝儀之位王族故士虎士在路門之右南靣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3099:3119'>大僕從者在路門之左南靣是在路門外也故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3119:3139'>知此外朝路門外之朝也此對路寢庭朝爲外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3139:3159'>朝若對庫門外朝朝士所掌三槐九棘之朝則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3159:3179'>此路門外朝亦爲内朝也故玉藻云朝於内朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3179:3199'>朝辨色始入君日岀而視之退適路寢是也其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3199:3219'>朝位天子之朝三公北靣東上孤東靣北上卿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3219:3239'>大夫西靣北上其士門西東靣北上若諸侯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3239:3259'>朝案大射卿西靣北上大夫北靣東上士門西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3259:3286'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-9a' );" name="007-9a" class="pb">[007-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3286:3297'>東靣北上與天子不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3297:3312'><span class='krp-note'>十/八</span>五牲屬五行馬屬火</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3312:3332'>案周禮雞人屬宗伯羊人屬司馬故此云司馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3332:3353'>奉羊犬人屬司㓂案五行傳云牛屬土雞屬木羊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3353:3373'>屬火犬屬金豕屬水司空冬官其位當水故鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3373:3393'>注周禮司空奉豕與案五行傳馬屬火而周禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3393:3410'>司馬羞馬牲者以其主馬故特使供之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3410:3426'><span class='krp-note'>十/九</span>一命再命齒三命不齒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3426:3446'>云一命齒于郷里者引黨正文解三命不踰父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3446:3473'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-9b' );" name="007-9b" class="pb">[007-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3473:3493'>兄之事也一命尚卑若與郷里長宿燕食則猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3493:3513'>計年也云再命齒于父族者再命漸尊不復與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3513:3533'>郷里計年唯官髙在上但父族爲重而猶與之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3533:3553'>計年爲列也云三命不齒者三命大貴則不復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3553:3573'>與父族計年若應有燕㑹則别席獨坐在賔之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3573:3577'>東也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3577:3592'><span class='krp-note'>二/十</span>貴宫貴室當是路寢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3592:3612'>下云下宮上云大廟此貴宫貴室旣非大廟又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3612:3632'>非下宮下室唯當路寢也指其院宇謂之宮指</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3632:3660'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-10a' );" name="007-10a" class="pb">[007-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3660:3680'>其所居之處謂之室爾雅云宫謂之室室謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3680:3700'>宫此貴宮貴室緫據路寢上云大廟此云下宮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3700:3720'>除大廟之外唯有親廟髙祖以下故云下宮親</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3720:3740'>廟也上云貴室此又云下室故知燕寢也云或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3740:3760'>言宫則下宮也成言廟則太廟也故春秋云立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3760:3780'>武宮明堂位云武公之廟武丗室也是通異語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3780:3783'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3783:3794'><span class='krp-note'>二/一</span>公族之刑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3794:3814'>公族其有死罪則磬于甸人其刑罪則纎剸亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3814:3842'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-10b' );" name="007-10b" class="pb">[007-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3842:3862'>告于甸人公族無宫刑獄成有司讞于公其死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='3862:3882'>罪則曰某之罪在大辟其刑罪則曰某之罪在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='3882:3902'>小辟公曰宥之有司又曰在辟公又曰宥之有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='3902:3922'>司又曰在辟及三宥不對走岀致刑于甸人公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='3922:3942'>又使人追之曰雖然必赦之有司對曰無及也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='3942:3962'>反命于公公素服不舉爲之變如其倫之䘮無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='3962:3982'>服親哭之注云不於市朝者隱之也甸人掌郊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='3982:4002'>野之官縣縊殺之曰磬纎讀爲殱殱刺也剸割</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4002:4022'>也宮割臏墨劓則皆以刀鋸刺割人體也告讀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4022:4050'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-11a' );" name="007-11a" class="pb">[007-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4050:4070'>爲鞠讀書用法曰鞠宫割滛刑成平也讞之言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4070:4090'>白也辟亦罪也宥寛也欲寛其罪出於刑也又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4090:4110'>復也對荅也先者君毎言宥則荅之以將更寛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4110:4130'>之至於三罪定不復荅走徃刑之爲君之恩無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4130:4150'>巳罪旣正不可宥乃欲赦之無宫刑重刑殺其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4150:4170'>類也白巳刑殺素服於凶事爲吉於吉事爲凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4170:4190'>非䘮服也君雖不服臣卿大夫死則皮弁錫衰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4190:4210'>以居徃弔當事則弁絰於士蓋疑衰同姓則緦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4210:4230'>衰以弔之今無服者不徃弔也倫謂親䟽之比</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4230:4258'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-11b' );" name="007-11b" class="pb">[007-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4258:4278'>也素服亦皮弁矣不徃弔爲位哭之而已君於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4278:4286'>臣使有司哭之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4286:4304'><span class='krp-note'>二/二</span>素服於凶事爲吉吉事爲凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4304:4324'>正義曰案下曲禮重素鄭云重素衣裳皆素謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4324:4344'>之重素素爲衣裳也此素服亦然也於凶事爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4344:4364'>吉者人以凶事用布今乃用素是比於凶事爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4364:4384'>吉也於吉事爲凶者吉時皮弁服白布深衣素</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4384:4404'>積裳以采爲領縁今唯素服衣裳是比吉事爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4404:4425'>凶也非如五服之限故云非䘮服也<span class='krp-note'>通前章</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4425:4453'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-12a' );" name="007-12a" class="pb">[007-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4453:4470'><span class='krp-note'>二/三</span>三老五更之名更或爲叟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4470:4490'>正義曰三老五更各一人蔡邕以爲更字爲叟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4490:4510'>叟老稱又以三老爲三人五更爲五人非鄭義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4510:4530'>也今所不取云皆年老更事致仕者三老亦有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4530:4550'>更名五更亦有老稱但尊此老名特屬三老耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4550:4570'>以其天子父兄所事故知致仕者知天子以父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4570:4590'>兄養之者以天子冕而緫干而舞執醬而饋是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4590:4596'>父兄事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4596:4616'><span class='krp-note'>二/口</span>凡教丗子及學士之時之官之處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4616:4644'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-12b' );" name="007-12b" class="pb">[007-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4644:4664'>凡學丗子及學士必時春夏學干戈秋冬學羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4664:4684'>籥皆於東序小樂正學干大胥賛之籥師學戈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4684:4704'>籥師丞賛之胥鼓南春誦夏弦大師詔之瞽宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4704:4724'>秋學禮執禮者詔之冬讀書典書者詔之禮在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4724:4744'>瞽宗書在上庠注云四時各有冝學士謂司徒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4744:4764'>論俊選所升於學者干盾也戈旬孑㦸也干戈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4764:4784'>萬舞象武也用動作之時學之羽籥籥舞象文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4784:4804'>也用安靜之時學之詩云左手執籥右手秉翟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4804:4824'>四人皆樂官之屬也通職秋冬亦學以羽籥小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4824:4852'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-13a' );" name="007-13a" class="pb">[007-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='4852:4872'>樂正樂師也周禮樂師掌國學之政敎國子小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='4872:4892'>舞大胥掌學士之版以待致諸子春入學舎菜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='4892:4912'>合舞秋頒學合聲籥師掌教國子舞羽吹籥南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='4912:4932'>南夷之樂也胥掌以六樂之㑹正舞位旄人教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='4932:4952'>夷樂則以鼔節之詩云以雅以南以籥不僣誦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='4952:4972'>謂歌樂也弦謂以絲播詩陽用事則學之以聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='4972:4992'>隂用事則學之以事因時順氣於功易也周立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='4992:5012'>三代之學學書於有虞氏之學典謨之教所興</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5012:5032'>也學舞於夏后氏之學文武中也學禮樂於殷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5032:5060'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-13b' );" name="007-13b" class="pb">[007-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5060:5080'>之學功成治定與己同也正義曰云學士謂司</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5080:5100'>徒論俊選所升於學者則王制云王子卿大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5100:5120'>元士之適子及國之俊選等升於學謂入學也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5120:5140'>故下云於東序是大學也誦謂歌樂者謂口誦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5140:5160'>歌樂之篇章不以琴瑟歌也云弦謂以絲播詩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5160:5180'>者謂以琴瑟播彼詩之音節詩音則樂章也若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5180:5200'>學舞之時春夏學干戈而用動秋冬學羽籥而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5200:5220'>用靜皆據年二十升於大學者若其未升大學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5220:5240'>之時則春誦夏弦在殷之瞽宗也云陽用事則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5240:5268'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-14a' );" name="007-14a" class="pb">[007-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5268:5288'>學之以聲春夏是陽陽主清輕故學聲聲亦清</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5288:5308'>輕云隂用事則學之以事秋冬屬隂隂主體質</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5308:5328'>故學事事亦體質因四時所冝順動靜之氣於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5328:5348'>學功業易成也云周立三代之學者謂立虞夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5348:5368'>殷學也其虞之學制在國兼在西郊郊則周之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5368:5388'>小學也夏殷之學亦在國而鄭注儀禮云周立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5388:5408'>四代之學於國者合周家爲言耳故與此注不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5408:5428'>同夏后氏之學在上庠即周之大學爲夏之制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5428:5448'>也云學書於虞氏之學興謨之教所興也者虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5448:5476'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-14b' );" name="007-14b" class="pb">[007-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5476:5496'>書有典有謨故就其學中而教之則周之小學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5496:5505'>也此已下追𥙷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5505:5524'><span class='krp-note'>二/五</span>教凡祭與養老乞言合語之禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5524:5544'>凡祭與養老乞言合語之禮皆小樂正詔之於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5544:5564'>東序注云學以三者之威儀也養老乞言養老</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5564:5584'>人之賢者因從乞善言可行者也合語謂郷射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5584:5604'>郷飲酒大射燕射之屬也郷射記曰古者於旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5604:5624'>也語正義曰學以三者學教也教以三者威儀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5624:5644'>容貌言祭與養老乞言及合語行禮之時皆有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5644:5672'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-15a' );" name="007-15a" class="pb">[007-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5672:5692'>容貌故小樂正教之云合語謂郷射郷飲酒大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5692:5712'>射燕射之屬三者此經先云祭與養老乞言別</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5712:5732'>云合語則合語非祭與養老也故知是郷射郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5732:5752'>飲酒及大射燕射之等指儀禮成文而言之以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5752:5772'>其此等至旅酬之時皆合語也其實祭末及養</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5772:5792'>老亦皆合語也故詩楚茨論祭祀之事云笑語</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5792:5812'>卒獲箋云古者旅也語是祭有合語也養老旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5812:5832'>乞言自然合語也引郷射記者證旅酬之時言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5832:5852'>說先王之法故云古者於旅也語言合語者謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5852:5880'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-15b' );" name="007-15b" class="pb">[007-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5880:5890'>合㑹義理而語說也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5890:5909'><span class='krp-note'>二/六</span>小樂正教威儀大樂正教義理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='5909:5929'>大樂正學舞干戚語說命乞言皆大樂正授數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='5929:5949'>注云學以三者之義也戚斧也語說合語之說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='5949:5969'>也數篇數正義曰前文小樂正旣教三者之威</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='5969:5989'>儀仐大樂正又教三者之義理故大樂正學舞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='5989:6009'>干前經云祭故養老乞言與祭相連故尊之序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6009:6029'>在合語之上此經不云祭故略其養老在語說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6029:6049'>之下皆大樂正授數者謂干戚語說乞言三者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6049:6077'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-16a' );" name="007-16a" class="pb">[007-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6077:6097'>皆大樂正之官授丗子及學士等篇章之數爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6097:6117'>之講說使知義理此經與前經重序其事文勢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6117:6137'>相似前經小樂正乃教威儀事淺故云詔之東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6137:6157'>序此大樂正所教義理旣深故大樂正授數知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6157:6177'>者文承東序之下大樂正授數之時亦在東序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6177:6197'><span class='krp-note'>二/七</span>天子成均飲酒郊人亦得酌上尊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6197:6218'>天子於成均之内飲酒以恩澤𬒳及於此郊人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6218:6238'>其郊人雖賤亦得取爵於堂上之尊以相旅也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6238:6258'>所以榮之凡飲酒之禮尊者酌於堂上之尊卑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6258:6286'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-16b' );" name="007-16b" class="pb">[007-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='6286:6306'>者酌於堂下之尊故特牲禮主人獻賔及獻衆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='6306:6326'>賔及長兄弟等及次賔及次兄弟等皆酌於堂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='6326:6346'>下之尊以相旅是也今郊人雖賤亦得酌於堂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='6346:6357'>上尊故云取爵於上尊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='6357:6376'><span class='krp-note'>二/八</span>丗子記是尋常丗子非文王法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='6376:6396'>丗子之記曰朝夕至于大寢之門外問於内豎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='6396:6416'>曰今日安否何如注云朝夕朝朝暮夕也日中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6416:6437'>又朝文王之爲丗子非禮之制丗子之禮亡言此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6437:6457'>存其記正義曰此等五節也文王爲丗子是聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6457:6485'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-17a' );" name="007-17a" class="pb">[007-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6485:6505'>人之法也不可以爲常行故此記㝷常丗子之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='6505:6509'>禮也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='6509:6518'>禮記要義卷第八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='6518:6546'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '007-17b' );" name="007-17b" class="pb">[007-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
